about the CLI which will talk to figlet gateway hosted at gopher protocol
.........................................................................

compile the user_command.c file using
      gcc user_command.c -o user_command.out

then compile gopher_server
      gcc gopher_server.c -o gopher_server.out

then run gopher_server 

     ./gopher_server.out

finally run user command another terminal
     ./user_command.out

CLI >> -h,---help   (HELP)
CLI >> -l ,--list-font  (list all font which is in gopher protocol)
CLI >> put any font which (display using CLI >> -l) e.g CLI >> <any_string> <space> <font>
                                                        CLI >> helpshift big
                                                        CLI >> HELPSHIFT small
                                                        CLI >> abc@123 lean

 
